<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="https://dcassetcdn.com/design_img/10150/25224/25224_294121_10150_image.jpg" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>Recipe List</title>
</head>
<body>
    <style>
        /* General body styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            background: white;
        }

        /* Header styling */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(34,17,223,1) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,1) 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        /* Recipe list container */
        .recipe-list {
            margin: 20px;
        }

        /* Set up the grid for the recipe list */
        .recipe-list ul {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Recipe list items */
        .recipe-list li {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .recipe-list li:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        /* Recipe list images */
        .recipe-list img {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        #addbtn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        #addbtn:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        /* Recipe list links */
        .recipe-list a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #ff6347;
        }

        /* Recipe list descriptions */
        .recipe-list p {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        #addbtn {
            display: block;
            margin: 20px auto;
            width: 200px;
            padding: 15px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #addbtn:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        /* Footer styling */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                padding: 15px;
            }

            .recipe-list {
                margin: 10px;
            }

            .recipe-list li {
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .recipe-list a {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .recipe-list p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            header {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .recipe-list {
                margin: 5px;
            }

            .recipe-list li {
                padding: 8px;
            }

            .recipe-list a {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .recipe-list p {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }

            footer {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
    <header>
        <h1>Snacks Recipes List</h1>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section class="recipe-list">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <img src="https://www.simplyrecipes.com/thmb/kFG0KjF0DYtVCSlkFivDSrUBpkg=/1600x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__simply_recipes__uploads__2019__12__Vegetable-Samosas-LEAD-1-65199bf0727346c8871b4b3d362da391.jpg" alt="Vegetable Samosa - a crispy, fried snack filled with spiced potatoes and peas">
                    <a class="page-title" data-title="Vegetable Samosa"href="/recipes">Vegetable Samosa</a>
                    <p>This vegetable samosa recipe is a classic Indian snack.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="https://womenshine.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images-78.jpeg" alt="Cheese Nuggets - a crispy snack made with cheese and spices">
                    <a class="page-title" data-title="Cheese Nuggets"href="/recipes">Cheese Nuggets</a>
                    <p>They make the perfect spicy sharing starter</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="http://www.oliviascuisine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/classic-pizza-margherita-1.jpg" alt="Margherita Pizza - a classic pizza topped with fresh mozzarella and basil">
                    <a class="page-title" data-title="Margherita Pizza"href="/recipes">Margherita Pizza</a>
                    <p>Pizza with perfectly melty mozzarella cheese and fresh basil.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="https://www.vegrecipesofindia.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/aloo-tikki-recipe-2-580x580.jpg" alt="Aloo Tikki - spiced potato patties">
                    <a class="page-title" data-title="Aloo Tikki"href="/recipes">Aloo Tikki</a>
                    <p>Learn how to make crispy and fluffy aloo tikki.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/92/d7/9b/92d79bdebda57262fd803118aa873d2d.jpg" alt="Vegetable Spring Rolls - flaky rolls filled with fresh vegetables">
                    <a class="page-title" data-title="Vegetable Spring Rolls" href="/recipes">Vegetable Spring Rolls</a>
                    <p>Stuffed with fresh vegetables and Noodles.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
    <button id="addbtn" onclick="location.href='/addrecipes'" style="padding: 10px; font-size: 16px;">Add Recipes</button>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Delicious Recipes. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
    <script>
        // Step 2: JavaScript to handle clicks
    document.querySelectorAll('.page-title').forEach(function(anchor) {
        anchor.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
            event.preventDefault(); // Prevent default anchor click behavior
            const title = this.getAttribute('data-title'); // Fetch the title
            const targetUrl = '/recipes?title=' + encodeURIComponent(title); // Construct the target URL
            window.location.href = targetUrl; // Redirect to the new page
        });
    });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
